From: Jihong Min <hurryman2212@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 1 Jun 2026 13:30:00 +0900
Subject: [PATCH] net: airoha: add SOE PPE flow support

Program PPE flow entries with the SOE tunnel metadata needed for inline
ESP encapsulation and decapsulation. This also keeps the bind-rate and
SOE commit probe-window knobs exposed so hardware flow binding behavior
can be tuned without rebuilding the kernel.

Assisted-by: Codex:gpt-5.5
Signed-off-by: Jihong Min <hurryman2212@gmail.com>
---
